UNIVERSITY OF NEVADA
Reno, Nevada
AUDIO VISUAL
COMMUNICATION CENTER
Pape 3
At the present time, KUNR-FM with 10 watts of power
is operating efficiently, furnishing proper training for students,
and broadcasting clearly throughout the Reno-Sparks area. Any increase
in power would not change any of these factors, but would only require
a needless additional expenditure.
KUNR-FM
